unting down. This shadow is not dependent on the sun, in fact, the shadow moves backwards no matter what time of day or night. There is only two problems… no one knows where the shadow began, or where it will end.%0a%3c %0a%3c %25lfloat text-align=center margin-top=5px margin-right=15px margin-bottom=5px margin-left=0px%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/mta/locations/oglethorpesquare3.jpg%0a%3c Because of this irregularity, [[Players.Siafu|Siafu]] has gained 24hr access to the nearby Oglethorpe Square House. It is [[Players.Siafu|Siafu]]’s belief, and now a belief shared by more than just a few members of the Consilium, that this square will be the next location for the Hallows created by [[Players.Hattan|Hattan]] battery. At least, that is what everyone is hoping. Because of this, the GoV keep watch over the square, and those who wish to study the sundial, the area, need speak first with [[Players.Siafu|Siafu]].%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Resonance:''' Unknown\\%0a%3c '''Territory:''' [[Guardians of the Veil]]%0a%3c [[#locationend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:include CityBook.Directory:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
